title: The Space
description: The year is 2096 ... Earth is doomed after the asteroid hit, and less than 5% of the population survived. And the survivors ventured out into space to find a new home... But on the way out of the solar system the ship crashed and needed urgent repairs at this time as asteroids and space debris slowly surrounded the ship. It was decided to deploy a small fighter, and that you'll fly! Your goal is to recapture asteroids and save the ship and its last traces of humanity!
